@startuml SD07_ListarProduto

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
title SD07 — Listar Produtos (com Estoque em Unidade Base)

actor "Usuário" as U
participant "ProductList\n(React)" as LIST
participant "ProductController\n(Spring)" as CTRL
participant "ProductService\n(Spring)" as SVC
participant "ProductRepository\n(JPA)" as REPO
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

U -> LIST : Acessa página de Produtos\nou clica "Atualizar Lista"

LIST -> CTRL : GET /product
CTRL -> SVC : findAll()
SVC -> REPO : findAll()
REPO -> DB : SELECT * FROM product
DB --> REPO : List<Product>
REPO --> SVC : List<Product>
SVC --> CTRL : List<ProductResponseDTO>\n{ id, name, code, price, sellPrice,\n  storage (BigDecimal), minStorage (BigDecimal),\n  categoryId, categoryName,\n  tipo, purchaseUnit, packageQuantity }
CTRL --> LIST : 200 OK + List<ProductResponseDTO>

LIST -> LIST : Renderiza tabela

note right of LIST
  Para coluna "Estoque", a função
  baseUnitOf(purchaseUnit) determina o sufixo:
  • G ou KG → "g"
  • ML ou L  → "ml"
  • UN/DUZIA → "un"
  • null      → "un."

  Badge vermelho se:
    storage <= minStorage
  Badge verde se:
    storage > minStorage
end note

LIST --> U : Tabela com badge colorido\nEx: "5000 g" (verde) ou "100 g" (vermelho)

@enduml